# Cloud Engineering Course (Sept 2024 - Mar 2025)

## 1. Cloud Computing Knowledge in AWS
- **Security in the Cloud**
  - IAM
  - CloudTrail
- **Cost Optimization**
  - Budget Creation
  - Cost Explorer
- **Compute Service**
  - EC2 (Instances, Features, Demo)
  - Lambda Functions
- **Storage Service**
  - Simple Storage Service (S3)
    - Storage Classes
    - Components
  - Elastic Block Storage
  - Elastic File System
- **Cloud Networking**
  - Virtual Private Network (VPC)
    - Subnets and Routing tables
    - Internet and NAT Gateway
    - Load balancing and Auto scaling
    - VPC flowlogs
  - CloudTrail
  - Route53
  - AWS Certificate Manager
  - Global Accelerator
- **Database**
  - AWS Relational Database
  - DynamoDB
- **Monitoring and Logging**
  - AWS CloudWatch
  - CloudTrail

## 2. Basics of Linux Operating System
- File System
- File permissions
- Basic Linux Commands
- Virtual Box
- Package and Software management

## 3. Version Control Systems
- Git
- GitHub
  - Branching and Merging Strategies
  - Peer reviews
  - Admin Setups

## 4. Infrastructure as Code [Terraform]
- Introduction to IaC
- Components of Terraform
- Terraform Basics
- Terraform implementation
- Terraform Blocks
  - Resource blocks
  - Provider Blocks
  - Variable blocks
- Terraform backend configuration
- Terraform Modules
- Terraform import

## 5. Containerization & Orchestration
- **Containerization**
  - Microservices
  - Docker Images
  - Docker Containers
  - Docker registry
  - Dockerfile
  - Container Volume mount
  - Docker Compose
- **Kubernetes**
  - Components of K8s
  - Kubernetes Deployments
  - ReplicaSets
  - Namespaces

## 6. CI/CD
- Jenkins installation (local machine and EC2)
- Pipeline as a Code with Jenkinsfile

## 7. Resume and Interview Preparation
